## Limitations

The findings are based on available online sources and may not fully capture the complexity of young people's attitudes towards communism. The data is limited to English-language sources and may not reflect global perspectives. Additionally, the reliance on opinion pieces and surveys means the findings are subject to biases inherent in these formats. Further research, including qualitative studies and interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding.